OL,3,CCar passenger, 17, dies with three
OL,4,Cothers seriously injured in crash
OL,6,FA teenager has died and three others
OL,7,Fhave been seriously injured in a car
OL,8,Fcrash at Beachy Head, Sussex.
OL,10,FA passenger in one of the cars, a boy,
OL,11,Faged 17 from Eastbourne, was confirmed
OL,12,Fdead at the scene.
OL,14,FTwo other men in the car, a 19-year-
OL,15,Fold man from Polegate and a 21-year-
OL,16,Fold man from Hellingly, were seriously
OL,17,Finjured.
OL,19,FThe driver of the other car, a man
OL,20,Faged 21, from Eastbourne, was also
OL,21,Fseriously injured.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/3
