OL,3,CCar passenger, 17, dies with three
OL,4,Cothers seriously injured in crash
OL,6,FThe collision, involving a blue VW
OL,7,FGolf and a white VW Polo, happened
OL,8,Fnear a layby by Shooters Bottom car
OL,9,Fpark at Beachy Head just before
OL,10,F9.30pm. on 26 June 2026.
OL,12,FDetective Sergeant Ian Foxton, from
OL,13,Fthe Serious Collision Investigation
OL,14,FUnit, said: "This is a tragic incident
OL,15,Fand are thoughts are with those
OL,16,Finvolved and their families.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/3
